{"tid":124632,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚緊急搵人","createTime":"2017-02-17T18:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T17:51:49.000Z","uid":83741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7bc8934f174125995a67d050d40be173325a1dd2","tid":124632,"uid":83741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:04:48.000Z","msg":"係咁的前日係大圍美田籃球場打波，我同我朋友個袋就比班死mk偷左入個銀包有親人既遺物係入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有好多有記念價值既野係入面，我朋友既最後一張同呀媽影既合照都係佢自己個袋到。依架有佢地電話同相，但就潛哂水，各位巴打絲打幫幫手睇下有冇方法搵到佢地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4c3bcbe36f490a319f1ad7dd80610e30fb5025","tid":124632,"uid":83741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:08:06.000Z","msg":"住大圍<br />\n叫坦克<br />\n[img]<img src=\"https://holland.pk/n8poatml\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fn8poatml&h=d928ff07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片網址[/img]中間果個<br />\n電話，69992768，93492313<br />\n住上水<br />\n叫細粒[img]<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lif4hwmz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flif4hwmz&h=667a40e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片網址[/img]<br />\n電話，56061745"},{"pid":"f1f6db2db917918694a40fdae513eba16acae3e3","tid":124632,"uid":80080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:24:14.000Z","msg":"借刀? 唔報警？"},{"pid":"ccb2f0a9b24ed391463087f97f0ddc2621e7f097","tid":124632,"uid":83741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:26:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借刀? 唔報警？</blockquote><br />\n報左，淨係想佢地如果冇放走部電話既話，交番出黎就當冇事"},{"pid":"48709ce06368b6057a1f6cfb483b3992711e43e7","tid":124632,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:49:06.000Z","msg":"係到叫有閪用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0042684144b5c14d889179a6e5d149a4d11d70f","tid":124632,"uid":69486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T22: